r=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104zga1665702688096.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zga1665702688096.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/zga1665702688096.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"zga1665702688096\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Font Range\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Number of available Uniface character sets (Font 0 through Font 7) for which a button is displayed when this panel is used as a session panel. Valid values are <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code> through <code class=\"ph codeph\">7</code>.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zga1665702688096__section_wqz_nlr_cxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d312407e57\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"zga1665702688096__p_d110423e1_d110424e1_d110425e1\">The character set buttons appear only if the panel is\n        used as a session panel on an application shell. They do not appear on a pop-up panel or a\n        form panel.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"zga1665702688096__section_dqn_4lr_cxb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d312407e66\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"zga1665702688096__ul_wdr_plr_cxb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"zga1665702688096__li_d42698e1_d42699e1_d42700e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"byf1705583062647.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/byf1705583062647.html\" title=\"Panels are global objects that are typically used to create toolbars for form components and application shells. They contain buttons to execute structure editor functions and activate component operations.\">Panels</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617362\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3617362\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Font Range Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Apr 26, 2023 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Font Range Number of available Uniface character sets (Font 0 through Font 7) for which a button is displayed when this panel is used as a session panel. Valid values are 0 through 7 . Description The character set buttons appear only if the panel is used as a session panel on an application shell. They do not appear on a pop-up panel or a form panel. Applies To Panels Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}